{
  "stem": "3659.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And during the time when we did a lot of traveling and all that, and my father also felt that if you learn a language you should go to the country.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we spent a whole summer in England, and we spent times with a partner of my father, who was in partners in business with him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lived with a family in England for three months in their home, and that was in 19-- in the summer of 1937.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the agreement was that the following summer, their children would come stay with us and so they would learn German language, which, of course, never came to pass.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we-- we came back from London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we also stayed in France for about three or four weeks with the same family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so it was delightful, because the languages were spoken, and it was something that we just enjoyed very much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My sister-- even though we were very young, we were two little ladies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We really were able to carry ourselves very well so we never were a burden to the family, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, 18 months difference, my sister and myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So during that period of time, we spent time together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were very close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we returned to Vienna, and that year, that '37, '38, we went on an quite a long vacation to-- in the, I believe, the Hungarian mountains there skiing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because that was also a big thing with us was sports, gymnastic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I skied, and I skated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we skated practically every day during the time we lived in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are very, very close to this very day.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
